    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 5.2 Train DepthAwareGATv2 (Anti-Collapse Architecture)\n",
        "\n",
        "This improved GAT model uses:\n",
        "1. **Skip connections**: Preserve original features through each layer\n",
        "2. **Jumping Knowledge (JKNet)**: Concatenate all layer representations\n",
        "3. **2 layers only**: Reduced from 3 to prevent over-smoothing\n",
        "4. **Layer normalization**: Stabilize training\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "# Train DepthAwareGATv2 model (anti-collapse architecture)\n",
        "print(\"=\" * 70)\n",
        "print(\"Training DepthAwareGATv2 (Skip Connections + JKNet + 2 Layers)\")\n",
        "print(\"=\" * 70)\n",
        "\n",
        "gat_v2_model, gat_v2_metrics = trainer.train(\n",
        "    model_name='depth_aware_gat_v2',\n",
        "    weight_decay=1e-3,\n",
        "    max_epochs=200,\n",
        "    patience=20,\n",
        "    verbose=True\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"\\nDepthAwareGATv2 Results:\")\n",
        "print(f\"  Test Macro F1: {gat_v2_metrics['test_macro_f1']:.4f} (treats classes equally)\")\n",
        "print(f\"  Test Balanced Acc: {gat_v2_metrics['test_balanced_acc']:.4f}\")\n",
        "print(f\"  Test MAE: {gat_v2_metrics['test_mae']:.4f} roots\")\n",
        "print(f\"  (Weighted F1: {gat_v2_metrics['test_f1']:.4f} - for comparison only)\")\n"
      ],
      "execution_count": 10,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "======================================================================\n",
            "Training DepthAwareGATv2 (Skip Connections + JKNet + 2 Layers)\n",
