        "## 6.5 Compare Classification vs Regression Baseline\n",
        "\n",
        "Train a regression model that predicts root count as a continuous value (0.0-4.0) and rounds to get class predictions. This tests whether the **ordinal structure** of root counts matters.\n",
        "\n",
        "**If regression beats classification** → root counts are ordinal, consider CORAL loss.\n"
      ]
    },
