        "## 6.8 Mini-Batch Training with Weighted Sampling\n",
        "\n",
        "Train using **NeighborLoader** + **WeightedRandomSampler** to oversample minority classes.\n",
        "This addresses class imbalance at the data level rather than just loss weighting.\n",
        "\n",
        "**Key benefits**:\n",
        "- Each mini-batch has roughly equal class representation\n",
        "- Better gradient signal for rare classes (3-4 roots)\n",
        "- Scales to larger graphs (samples k-hop neighborhoods)\n"
      ]
    },
